reviewText: Savion Glover is a genius as are the musicians he riffs with.  However, I found it difficult to watch the tapping on camera without being there - it's not the same as seeing it live.  However, genius is genius.
Savion is talented but not an entertainer. Boring.
Love to watch Savion Dance.  He is obviously passionate about what he does, but sometimes he talks in circles and it gets a little slow, especially the beginning.  Strong finish!!
